I"<h1 class="no_toc" id="logging-in-to-irida">Logging in to IRIDA</h1>

<p>After an administrator or manager has created a user account for you in IRIDA, you‚Äôll be able to log in.</p>

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="#logging-in-for-the-first-time" id="markdown-toc-logging-in-for-the-first-time">Logging in for the first time</a></li>
  <li><a href="#logging-in-after-your-first-login" id="markdown-toc-logging-in-after-your-first-login">Logging in after your first login</a></li>
